m\": \"that world record\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"holder\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meadows, who thinks 2026 might be a better target, added: \\\"We are definitely nudging our way towards it.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meadows\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"a better target\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"our way\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A couple of years ago we would never have been looking at that world record thinking it was possible, but now you start getting a little bit giddy and excited, but trying to be realistic at the same time.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"that world record thinking\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Gold is the only currency she wants to work in now, and she's got some personal objectives to win that world title.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"the only currency\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"some personal objectives\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"that world title\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think she's looking at it as though it's really exciting, whether we can get physically in world record shape next year.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world record shape\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"1:53.28 is still a big, big gap.\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1:53.28\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2374}, {\"ngram\": \"a big, big gap\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know Keely would 